  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large paella pan or skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion, carrot, and celery and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the smoked paprika, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine.",
    "Add the masarepa and cook for 2 minutes, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the eggs and cook until the eggs are set.",
    "Remove from heat and let rest for 5 minutes before serving."
